title: Rewind: Bow wow / Luenell Interview and more

description:
Friday 7/6 -Today on the show we revisited the time that Bow- Wow stopped by where he addressed the #BowWowChallenge And Addresses Rumors In His Last Radio Interview with The Breakfast Club. Also, we revisited the time comedian Luenell stopped by and got nasty on The Breakfast Club, spoke Insta-Comics, Wendy Williams, and even attempts to spill the tea on some things. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a superintendent who was charged with lewdness, public urination and defecation.
